  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Fix Map Column Responsiveness on Contact Page\n\nThe map component on the contact page is only sized with col-lg-7, which causes it to display too small on mobile devices. Update the responsive grid classes to ensure proper display across all screen sizes.\n\nRequirements:\n- Add appropriate Bootstrap column classes for mobile (col-12 or col-sm-*) and tablet (col-md-*) breakpoints\n- Ensure the map displays at full width on mobile devices for better usability\n- Maintain the existing col-lg-7 layout for large desktop screens\n- Verify the map height is appropriate on mobile devices\n- Test the layout on multiple breakpoints (mobile, tablet, desktop) to ensure smooth responsive behavior\n- Ensure any adjacent content (contact form, info, etc.) also responds appropriately to the grid changes",
